00:33:56,491 --> 00:33:59,783
These are smoke bombs,
and those two are full of nails.

368
00:34:01,408 --> 00:34:04,033
They're gonna work this time, I know it.

369
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:06,741
Me too.

370
00:34:14,533 --> 00:34:18,575
You know, Powder,
what makes you different makes you strong.

371
00:34:19,450 --> 00:34:21,283
Always remember that, okay?

372
00:34:28,991 --> 00:34:32,616
What the hell were you thinking,
going into The Last Drop?

373
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:36,616
- Do you have any idea what you've done?
- I was getting results!

374
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:39,116
- You heard the Council.
- You're a fool.

